sentences: Halina Mlynkova (born 22 June 1977 in Návsí) is a Polish singer originally from the Czech Republic.
From 1998 to 2003, she was the vocalist of a popular Polish folk-rock group Brathanki.
She was married to Polish actor Łukasz Nowicki for nine years.

Since February 2015 she is married to the Czech music producer Lešek Wronka.
